{"type": "article", "id": 5449, "title": "Andy Warhol x Converse 联名帆布鞋", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-22T07:29:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233858ALIroKQcnJyCeF31.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t匡威日前联手已故波普艺术家 Andy Warhol 名下基金会，推出最新联名系列新作，这一系列鞋子以匡威经典的 Chuck Taylor All Star 鞋款为设计基础，鞋面上施以 Andy Warhol 生前创作的波普版画，包括金宝汤以及各式人像作品，均以印花的形式呈现出来，街头艺术感十足。这一系列联名鞋款提供低筒、高筒以及女士高跟 3 种款型，售价 60－90 美元（约合人民币 373－559元），将于 2 月 7 日起在各匡威门店与<a href=\"http://www.converse.com/\" target=\"_blank\">线上商店</a>同步发售。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233856Jz8ulmSfbdOpNQvG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233856pDjXBFCUWNkE2mQG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233857YSNmfwtTiHqzDEWZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233857irjDkAe4FQ9p8MoK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233858zIOvopcu2yXHNDmg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233858UduhHQ42bY1O5KDf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}